Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.54,0:02:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想保护结花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.30,0:02:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好啦  结花她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫血？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  只是贫血而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了没事的  可香央里她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你是在教室里昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过没什么大碍了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微睡一会儿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个来  我更担心驱君你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.43,0:02:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.79,0:02:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那素描簿…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西到底意味着什么  到时候自然就会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么在意也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.31,0:03:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在意？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别对我说谎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么亲热  不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得人背上痒痒  真是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一点儿都不可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没看见前面…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿一包走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水奈濑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  彩子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是睡眠不足  原因是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟你也是个花季少女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  不好好睡的话可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.32,0:05:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  要是又睡不着了的话  就叫人给你唱摇篮曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？摇篮曲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吗  臯月？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我唱？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话上唱就好啦  就唱给她听嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我…摇篮曲什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始是有点不好意思  不过很快就会习惯了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也是这样的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩子老师也唱…  摇篮曲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  很奇怪么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给谁唱呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  有小孩呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不也见过么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个一点都不可爱的不良少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大婶  老规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们吃惊个什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  感觉不太搭调？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也难怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不是亲生的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话  我就算是养母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养母…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前啊  我可是个有点我行我素的摩托车爱好者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我行我素的…  爱好者？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  女飚车族么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算…简单说来就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  那一夜也发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被条子追着…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.47,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是所谓的流浪儿童吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是小孩  但还是拼命地想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但孩子毕竟还是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候  我突然想到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来保护这孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:07:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来那时我也是年少轻狂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可真后悔当初捡了那样一个包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流浪儿童…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟在孤儿院长大的我们一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  你们也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要叫他给你唱摇篮曲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  结花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会给我唱的吧  驱君？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住  站住  站住…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的乖猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡  不注意的话可会很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  刚一说就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心  这可是个暴力小猫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  喵  喵…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人我不告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来保护这孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.07,0:09:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学以后  也要拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天呢  在那之前  我要给你们介绍一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  前辈你说过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她似乎终于下定决心要见你们了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君  练剑就等你们见完了面再开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那放学之后  考现学部见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为  为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘记说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.75,0:10:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久前辈从今天起  就成为我们考现学部的一员了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是你跟我说能够随便山吃海喝  这我才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抹布  抹布  抹布…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.71,0:11:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了啦  不得了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  现在我向大家介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年级B班的橘菊理同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  她跟臯月君你的姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在无意间见到过了好几次  每次都心里七上八下的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为长得一模一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理同学她不会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵能听见声音  所以别人说的还是能懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要对话的时候  就只能笔谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想大家应该很快就能适应了才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫广原雪子  请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊前辈  好丰满的胸部  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fa do sete o furese en tora
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可还真是吓了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么啊  刚才那话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是Fa do sete o furese en tora
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外语？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的故乡德拉斯贝尼亚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是  为了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:12:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你硬要问怎么样  也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是口号了啦  我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口号？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用在「要加油哦」这样的时候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得还是有的好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准还挺不错的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是的说  为了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好  挺不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.87,0:13:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是的说  就是的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理前辈  觉得好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是败给了雪子你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了朋友和明日…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱前辈你也中意么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那就大家一起喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了么  一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群智障
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么口号啊  又不是三岁小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  贤久前辈居然害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把他给拉回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管他啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不是我们的战友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理学姐她名字跟姐姐一样  的确让人有点吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总算不是一个人  放心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了朋友和明日…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友  明日什么的  我从来就没有好好想过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉心里一紧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一句很响亮的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了朋友和明日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.09,0:14:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有见过  驱君的笑容了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得  好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结花…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只针对我吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊理学姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说  是去厕所了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看就来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草壁前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请指导我练剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君  今天已经很晚了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.20,0:16:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿练？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩到了就会滑倒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.51,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架势一旦崩溃  就全盘皆输了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对敌人  你不过就是只无头苍蝇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是现在  迄今为止  你都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想要保护结花」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这信念就横亘在你的眼前  于是你便不顾周围的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你首先得冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是之后一切的先决条件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心浮气躁的人  与胜利无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我把那些碎片消灭干净
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片们  我要把你们剁成肉酱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪里去了呢  菊理前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会出事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤久前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门之前可得先敲门哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里可是…  女厕所哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭你能打倒我么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我一根寒毛也伤不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就睁大眼睛好好看着  你想要保护的人的下场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后好好感受一下自己的无力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…  不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来…  别…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你无论怎样都想先去投胎的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就成全你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量差距太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从正面进攻不可能赢  只会被干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…  到底该怎么做  才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乌丸天国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你首先得冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心浮气躁之人  与胜利无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  不能慌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？废物  放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓破了胆  变得不正常了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.34,0:20:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将感情化为力量  只想着这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将感情…  化为力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护好结花的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然躲过去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛…  难不成…  没这种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种低贱的人类  是没有可能觉醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的铠甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回是伊拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉泽特  你刚才说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱…  驱君…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.69,0:22:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话呀  驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.06,0:22:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱君
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.78,0:24:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于觉醒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颤抖吧  为自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那瞳眸给予了你一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.68,0:24:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会夺走你一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.28,0:24:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你深爱的世界  深爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.07,0:24:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.08,0:24:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名维拉德  毁灭之国的王
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被劫之眼魅惑之人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(265,325)\fs17}AION
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.57,0:24:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.88,0:24:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乱我心者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.00,0:24:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在噩梦的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.45,0:24:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有答案吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
